CustomField.formula: IF( Maintenance_Returned_R__c = Maintenance_R__c , Maintenance_R__c, IF(Maintenance_Returned_R__c < Maintenance_R__c, Maintenance_R__c - Maintenance_Returned_R__c, Maintenance_R__c))
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This field denotes the number of tools that are in maintenance condition.
CustomField.label: Maintenance
